27 4-120-101. Title.
28 This chapter shall be known and may be cited as the "Retail Convenience
29 Store Security Act".
30
31 4-120-102. Legislative findings.
32 The General Assembly finds that:
33 (1) Retail convenience stores are convenient for both criminals
34 and consumers alike;
35 (2) Retail convenience stores have long been targets for
36 nighttime robberies and other crimes;
